Fit Simple Mediation Model for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution with Data Missing Completely at Random - 30% - Structural Equation Modeling

Source: R/mvn_mcar_30_unstd_fit.sem.R
mvn_mcar_30_fit.sem.Rd

Fit Simple Mediation Model for Data Generated from a Multivariate Normal Distribution with Data Missing Completely at Random - 30% - Structural Equation Modeling

mvn_mcar_30_fit.sem(data, taskid)

Arguments

data

n by 3 matrix or data frame. data[, 1] correspond to values for x. data[, 2] correspond to values for m. data[, 3] correspond to values for y.
taskid

Numeric. Task ID.
